+true command
+============
+
+Synopsis
+--------
+
+::
+
+    true
+
+Description
+-----------
+
+The true command sets the return value $? to 0 (true).
+
+Example
+-------
+
+::
+
+    => true; echo $?
+    0
+    =>
+
+Configuration
+-------------
+
+The true command is only available if CONFIG_HUSH_PARSER=y.
